After a small break for the holidays here we are with our first 2016 release. The 5th wave. We used the russian
version which was not to bad but not perfect. It had all kinds of pixelation and that flicker. Well we fixed the
pixelation and towned down the flickering but we couldnt eliminate it to much because then you would get some weird
artefacts. The we adjusted all the colors and gama contrast and toned down the bright spots as best as we could. 
Finally we added grain to it and sharpened it so we could mantain the details of the pic. As always check
sample as screens always look better
